c: 7
v: 160
t: "Men senndi Й“e gori sappo e Й—iЙ—i mofte. Men wahyini e Muusaa tuma nde yimЙ“e makko Й“en Й—aЙ“Й“irnoo mo yarnineede wonnde : \"Piyir tuggordu maa ndun hayre nden\". ЖҒulli sappo e Й—iЙ—i yallti e mayre. GomЙ—ii gorol kala andii yariride mu'un. Men Й—owdinirani Й“e duule, Men Jippini e maЙ“Й“e demmbe-njuuri, e teewu colli. \"Г‘aamee e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Men arsiki on\". ЖҒe tooГұaali Men, kono ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й“e tooГұaynoo"